{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01JSMB96pUDBdX1qos4yF5wx","type":"tool_result","content":"  3810→- **Duration:** Multiple sessions across multiple days\n  3811→\n  3812→The project delivered: stack detection (Node.js, Python, Rust), multi-stack support, observability enforcement, Docker integration, verification tiers, autonomous execution via Ralph, and comprehensive documentation — all verified to acceptance criteria.\n  3813→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01A9XPq7LBDxmxSgCKUFxewS","session_id":"c3549884-84b1-49d0-b5ba-29ed204ec9b6","uuid":"0c2997e7-ee4f-448e-b184-b448a3185fde","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:00:39.822Z"}
